ZH: 1. 我们的目标是消灭贫困。
EN: Our goal is to eradicate poverty.
ZH: 2. 这场战争的目的是消灭恐怖分子。
EN: The purpose of this war is to eliminate terrorists.
ZH: 3. 他们采取了一系列措施来消灭犯罪活动。
EN: They have taken a series of measures to eradicate criminal activities.
ZH: 4. 为了保护环境，我们需要消灭污染源。
EN: To protect the environment, we need to eliminate sources of pollution.
ZH: 5. 这个国家的政府决定消灭腐败现象。
EN: The government of this country has decided to eliminate corruption.
ZH: 6. 我们需要全力以赴来消灭世界上的饥饿问题。
EN: We need to do everything we can to eradicate hunger in the world.
ZH: 7. 这个项目的目标是消灭儿童文盲。
EN: The goal of this project is to eliminate child illiteracy.
ZH: 8. 我们希望未来能消灭种族歧视。
EN: We hope to eliminate racial discrimination in the future.
ZH: 9. 政府正在努力消灭非法贸易。
EN: The government is making efforts to eliminate illegal trade.
ZH: 10. 他们的团队被认为是消灭传染病的专家。
EN: Their team is considered experts in eradicating infectious diseases.
ZH: 11. 为了保护大熊猫，我们需要消灭栖息地的破坏。
EN: To protect pandas, we need to eliminate the destruction of their habitats.
ZH: 12. 这个社会需要消灭对性别的歧视。
EN: This society needs to eliminate gender discrimination.
ZH: 13. 他们合力消灭了敌人的阵地。
EN: They joined forces to eliminate the enemy's position.
ZH: 14. 这项任务要求我们消灭所有恶意软件。
EN: This mission requires us to eliminate all malicious software.
ZH: 15. 现代医学的发展有助于消灭一些传染病。
EN: The advancement of modern medicine contributes to the eradication of some infectious diseases.
ZH: 16. 消灭邪教是国家的一项重要任务。
EN: Eradicating cults is an important task for the country.
ZH: 17. 为了达到健康目标，你需要消灭不健康的习惯。
EN: To achieve your health goals, you need to eliminate unhealthy habits.
ZH: 18. 这个政策的目标是消灭贫困地区的落后现象。
EN: The goal of this policy is to eliminate backwardness in poverty-stricken areas.
ZH: 19. 只有通过教育，我们才能消灭无知。
EN: Only through education can we eliminate ignorance.
ZH: 20. 社会需要消灭对身体残疾人的歧视。
EN: Society needs to eliminate discrimination against people with physical disabilities.
